      "scrollWidth": 375,
      "textStart": "KITCHENPERMIT FOR HOOD CLEANING COMPANIES Send a restaurant-ready service report after every hood cleaning job. Turn job photos, blocked access notes, and next actions into one branded link/PDF the restaurant can save for inspection records. Try free builder View sample report Set up company reports Free: No login. Unbranded 7-day test link and watermarked PDF. Company: $79/mo. Your logo/contact, clean PDFs, live links, and history. SAMPLE SERVICE REPORT FROM THE FIELD What the crew sends in JOB PHOTOS Hood, filter, fan, and access photos OPEN ITEM Rear access panel blocked NEXT ACTION Clear access before the next visit WHAT THE RESTAURANT GETS One report, ready to save WORK RESULT Reachable hood, filters, and duct path cleaned PHOTO EVIDENCE Before/after photos grouped by hood area OPEN ITEM Blocked access kept separate from completed work SAVED COPY Link/PDF for inspection records AFTER SERVICE The cleaning is done. The customer still needs the record. RESTAURANT Sees what was done, what is still open, and what to save. HOOD COMPANY Looks organized without rewriting photo texts after the crew leaves. OFFICE Gets a cleaner service report for revisit, records, or follow-up. WHAT TH",
      "title": "Service reports for hood cleaning jobs | KitchenPermit",
      "url": "http://127.0.0.1:8096/"
    },
