      "scrollWidth": 375,
      "textStart": "KITCHENPERMIT FOR HOOD SERVICE VENDORS Send a branded service report after every hood cleaning job. Restaurant clients get one clean link/PDF they can save for inspections, with photos, open items, and the next action. VIEW SAMPLE REPORT SET UP COMPANY REPORTS See how this would look for my company Try free builder BRANDED SERVICE REPORT + PDF Restaurant-ready service report BRANDED RECORD Vendor logo, contact, job result, and PDF copy in one report. INSPECTION FILE Restaurant client can save the link/PDF with service reports. NEXT ACTION Photos, open items, and the next service step stay clear. NEXT STEP Clear the blocked area or confirm the next visit window. WHY VENDORS PAY The customer can understand the job and save the record for files. WHAT CHANGES AFTER EACH VISIT The customer should not need a callback to understand the job. The visit ends with one readable service report that explains what was done, what stayed open, and what the customer needs to do next. CUSTOMER SEES One branded service report link/PDF they can save with restaurant files. VENDOR GETS A same-day service report that makes the job easier to trust, file, and defend. WHY VENDORS BUY IT The first value is fe",
